---
pagination:
  data: stores.pages
  size: 1
  alias: store
permalink: "/{{ store.region }}/{{ store.slug }}/{{ store.channel_suffix }}index.html"
eleventyComputed:
  title: "{{ store.name_full_en }}"
  is_reserve_ready: "{{ 'true' if store.tablecheck_url != 'TBD' else 'false' }}"
  is_form_reserve: "{{ 'true' if store.reserve_system == 'form' else 'false' }}"
  tablecheck_with_utm: "{% if store.tablecheck_url != 'TBD' %}{{ store.tablecheck_url }}?utm_source={{ store.channel_utm_source }}&utm_medium=referral{% else %}#{% endif %}"
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="scroll-smooth" lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>{{ store.name_full_en }}</title>
<meta name="description" content="Muslim-friendly omakase featuring ultra-rare lean Wagyu and authentic Edomae sushi in {{ store.city }}. Alcohol-free menu, crafted for everyone.">
{% if store.channel_id != "default" %}
<meta name="robots" content="noindex,follow">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://{{ stores.brand.domain }}/{{ store.region }}/{{ store.slug }}/">
{% endif %}

<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) - GA4 -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id={{ stores.brand.ga4_id }}"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', '{{ stores.brand.ga4_id }}', {
    'store_name': '{{ store.slug }}',
    'store_area': '{{ store.region }}',
    'brand': '{{ stores.brand.brand_slug }}',
    'channel': '{{ store.channel_id }}'
  });
</script>

{% if store.google_ads_id %}
<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id={{ store.google_ads_id }}"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());

  gtag('config', '{{ store.google_ads_id }}');
</script>
{% endif %}

<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Epilogue:wght@300;400;600&family=Josefin+Sans:wght@300;400;600&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

<script>
tailwind.config = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        'ginza-gold': '#c9a96e',
        'ginza-black': '#090909',
        'ginza-ivory': '#f0ede4',
        'halal-green': '#0d1f10',
      },
      fontFamily: {
        'epilogue': ['Epilogue', 'sans-serif'],
        'cormorant': ['Cormorant Garamond', 'serif'],
        'josefin': ['Josefin Sans', 'sans-serif'],
      },
      animation: { 'ken-burns': 'kenburns 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate' },
      keyframes: {
        kenburns: { '0%': { transform:'scale(1)' }, '100%': { transform:'scale(1.15)' } }
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style>
body { padding-bottom: 72px; }
.reveal { opacity:0; transform:translateY(30px); transition:all 0.8s ease-out; }
.reveal.active { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
.dark-overlay { background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(9,9,9,0.15) 0%,rgba(9,9,9,0.90) 100%); }
.nav-link { position:relative; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(240,237,228,0.6); transition:color 0.3s; }
.nav-link::after { content:''; position:absolute; left:0; bottom:-2px; width:0; height:1px; background:#c9a96e; transition:width 0.3s; }
.nav-link:hover { color:#c9a96e; }
.nav-link:hover::after { width:100%; }
.header-divider { width:1px; height:14px; background:rgba(201,169,110,0.3); }
.sticky-cta { position:fixed; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:100; background:rgba(9,9,9,0.93); backdrop-filter:blur(12px); border-top:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.25); padding:12px 20px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; }
.sticky-cta-text { font-size:11px; color:rgba(240,237,228,0.55); letter-spacing:0.05em; line-height:1.4; }
.sticky-cta-text strong { display:block; color:rgba(201,169,110,0.9); font-weight:600; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; }
.sticky-cta-btn { flex-shrink:0; background:#c9a96e; color:#090909; font-family:'Josefin Sans',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; padding:12px 20px; border-radius:8px; white-space:nowrap; transition:transform 0.2s,opacity 0.2s; border:none; cursor:pointer; text-decoration:none; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; }
.sticky-cta-btn:hover { transform:scale(1.04); opacity:0.92; }
.halal-cert-badge { display:inline-flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:6px; border:1.5px solid #c9a96e; border-radius:50%; width:88px; height:88px; justify-content:center; position:relative; background:radial-gradient(circle at center,rgba(201,169,110,0.08) 0%,transparent 70%); }
.halal-cert-badge::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:4px; border-radius:50%; border:0.5px dashed rgba(201,169,110,0.4); }
.halal-cert-badge-wrap { display:flex; gap:20px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:2rem; }
.map-wrapper { position:relative; width:100%; padding-bottom:56.25%; height:0; overflow:hidden; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2); }
.map-wrapper iframe { position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; border:0; filter:grayscale(30%) contrast(1.05); }
.jp-text { font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.15em; }
.year-badge { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:3.5rem; color:rgba(201,169,110,0.2); line-height:1; }
.section-label { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.3em; color:rgba(201,169,110,0.6); text-transform:uppercase; }
.slide { transition: opacity 1.2s ease-in-out; }
.course-scroll { display:flex; gap:16px; overflow-x:auto; padding:8px 0 16px; -ms-overflow-style:none; scrollbar-width:none; }
.course-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
.course-card { flex-shrink:0; width:260px; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; }
@media (min-width:768px) {
  .course-scroll { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); overflow-x:visible; }
  .course-card { width:auto; }
}
.course-detail-panel { max-height:0; overflow:hidden; transition:max-height 0.4s ease; }
.course-detail-panel.open { max-height:600px; }
.chevron-icon { transition:transform 0.3s; }
.chevron-icon.open { transform:rotate(180deg); }
.booking-pulse { display:inline-block; width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; background:#ef4444; margin-right:8px; animation: pulseRed 1.8s ease-in-out infinite; box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.7); }
@keyframes pulseRed {
  0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.7); }
  70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0); }
  100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(239, 68, 68, 0); }
}
.review-scroll { display:flex; gap:16px; overflow-x:auto; padding:8px 0 16px; -ms-overflow-style:none; scrollbar-width:none; scroll-snap-type:x mandatory; }
.review-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
.review-card { flex-shrink:0; width:300px; padding:24px; border-radius:16px; border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2); background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,169,110,0.06) 0%, rgba(201,169,110,0.02) 100%); scroll-snap-align:start; }
@media (min-width:768px) {
  .review-scroll { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr); overflow-x:visible; }
  .review-card { width:auto; }
}
@media (min-width:1024px) {
  .review-scroll { grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr); }
}
</style>
</head>

<body class="bg-ginza-black text-ginza-ivory font-epilogue overflow-x-hidden">

<!-- STICKY CTA -->
<div class="sticky-cta">
  <div class="sticky-cta-text">
    <strong>Reservations</strong>
    Recommended 2 weeks in advance
  </div>
  {% if store.is_form_reserve == 'true' or is_form_reserve == 'true' %}
  <button onclick="openReserveModal('sticky_cta')" class="sticky-cta-btn"
          data-ga-event="reserve_click" data-ga-location="sticky_cta">
    RESERVE →
  </button>
  {% else %}
  <a href="{{ tablecheck_with_utm }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="sticky-cta-btn"
     data-ga-event="reserve_click" data-ga-location="sticky_cta">
    RESERVE →
  </a>
  {% endif %}
</div>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full z-50 bg-ginza-black/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-ginza-gold/20">
<div class="hidden sm:flex items-center justify-center gap-6 py-1.5 border-b border-ginza-gold/10 text-[9px] tracking-[0.25em] text-ginza-gold/60 uppercase">
<span>{{ store.region_label }}</span>
<span class="header-divider"></span>
<span>Open {{ store.hours }}</span>
<span class="header-divider"></span>
<span>Muslim-Friendly</span>
</div>
<nav class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-3 max-w-[390px] mx-auto">
<div class="flex flex-col leading-none">
<span class="text-[9px] tracking-[0.35em] text-ginza-gold/60 uppercase mb-0.5 jp-text">omakase</span>
<span class="text-xl text-ginza-gold tracking-wide jp-text">墨</span>
</div>
<div class="hidden xs:flex items-center gap-4">
<a class="nav-link" href="#story">Story</a>
<span class="header-divider"></span>
<a class="nav-link" href="#access">Access</a>
</div>
{% if store.is_form_reserve == 'true' or is_form_reserve == 'true' %}
<button onclick="openReserveModal('header')"
        class="bg-ginza-gold text-ginza-black px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-[10px] font-josefin font-semibold tracking-widest hover:bg-opacity-90 hover:scale-105 transition-all"
        data-ga-event="reserve_click" data-ga-location="header">
  RESERVE
</button>
{% else %}
<a href="{{ tablecheck_with_utm }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
   class="bg-ginza-gold text-ginza-black px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-[10px] font-josefin font-semibold tracking-widest hover:bg-opacity-90 hover:scale-105 transition-all"
   data-ga-event="reserve_click" data-ga-location="header">
  RESERVE
</a>
{% endif %}
</nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="relative h-screen w-full flex flex-col justify-end items-center overflow-hidden" id="hero">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<div id="slideshow" class="absolute inset-0">
<img class="slide absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="Omakase Full Course"/>
<img class="slide absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-0" src="/images/sushi.jpg" alt="Omakase Sushi"/>
<img class="slide absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-0" src="/images/wagyu.jpg" alt="A5 Wagyu"/>
<img class="slide absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-0" src="/images/Seasonal_menu.jpg" alt="Seasonal Menu"/>
<img class="slide absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-0" src="/images/Japanese_sweets.jpg" alt="Japanese Sweets"/>
</div>
<div class="absolute inset-0 dark-overlay"></div>
</div>

<div class="relative z-10 w-full px-8 pb-28 text-center">
<span class="inline-block border border-ginza-gold/50 px-3 py-1 mb-6 text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] text-ginza-gold uppercase jp-text">浅草 · ASAKUSA · TOKYO</span>
<h1 class="font-cormorant italic text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-3 leading-tight">
{{ store.name_full_en }}<br/><span class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">{{ store.name_zh }}</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-ginza-gold/60 tracking-widest mb-5 jp-text">おまかせコース · 和牛体験</p>
<p class="text-sm font-light text-ginza-ivory/70 mb-8 max-w-xs mx-auto leading-relaxed">
Ultra-rare lean Wagyu. Muslim-friendly.<br/>A dining experience crafted for the world.
</p>

<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 w-full max-w-xs mx-auto">
  {% if store.is_form_reserve == 'true' or is_form_reserve == 'true' %}
  <button onclick="openReserveModal('hero')"
     class="w-full bg-ginza-gold text-ginza-black font-josefin font-semibold rounded-lg tracking-widest text-sm hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(201,169,110,0.3)] flex overflow-hidden"
     data-ga-event="reserve_click" data-ga-location="hero">
    <span class="flex-1 py-4 px-4 text-center">RESERVE YOUR SEAT</span>
    <span class="bg-black/15 px-4 flex items-center justify-center">
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
        <path d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 21 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 5.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 21 11.25v7.5" stroke="#090909" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </span>
  </button>
  {% else %}
  <a href="{{ tablecheck_with_utm }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
     class="w-full bg-ginza-gold text-ginza-black font-josefin font-semibold rounded-lg tracking-widest text-sm hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-[0_0_24px_rgba(201,169,110,0.3)] flex overflow-hidden"
     data-ga-event="reserve_click" data-ga-location="hero">
    <span class="flex-1 py-4 px-4 text-center">RESERVE YOUR SEAT</span>
    <span class="bg-black/15 px-4 flex items-center justify-center">
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
        <path d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 21 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 5.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 21 11.25v7.5" stroke="#090909" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </span>
  </a>
  {% endif %}

  <a class="w-full text-center text-ginza-gold font-josefin text-xs tracking-widest py-3 rounded-lg border border-ginza-gold/40 hover:border-ginza-gold/80 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
     href="#access" data-ga-event="map_click" data-ga-location="hero">
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
      <path d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" stroke="#c9a96e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <path d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" stroke="#c9a96e" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    </svg>
    ACCESS &amp; MAP
  </a>

  <!-- BOOKING COUNT BANNER -->
  <div class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-ginza-gold/10 via-ginza-gold/20 to-ginza-gold/10 border border-ginza-gold/40 rounded-full px-4 py-2.5 mt-1">
    <span class="booking-pulse"></span>
    <span class="text-[11px] font-josefin font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] text-ginza-gold uppercase">
      <span class="text-ginza-ivory">76 bookings</span> in the last 24 hours
    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/20">
    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ginza-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L4.5 20.29l.71.71L12 18l6.79 3 .71-.71z"/></svg>
    <span class="text-[10px] font-josefin tracking-widest uppercase">Muslim-Friendly · Alcohol Free</span>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<script>
(function() {
const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.slide');
let current = 0;
setInterval(() => {
slides[current].style.opacity = '0';
current = (current + 1) % slides.length;
slides[current].style.opacity = '1';
}, 4000);
})();
</script>

<!-- MENU -->
<section class="reveal py-16 bg-ginza-black" id="menu">
<div class="text-center mb-10 px-6">
<p class="section-label mb-4">Menu · Mastery</p>
<h3 class="font-cormorant italic text-3xl mb-4 leading-snug">"Where Theatre Meets Taste"</h3>
<p class="text-sm font-light leading-relaxed text-ginza-ivory/70 max-w-lg mx-auto">
From the delicate assembly of Edomae-style sushi to the dramatic carving of A5 Wagyu, every course is a choreographed masterpiece performed live before your eyes.
</p>
</div>
<div class="flex mb-10">
<div class="relative flex-1 h-52 overflow-hidden group">
<img alt="Omakase Sushi" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" src="/images/sushi.jpg"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-ginza-black/70"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 p-4 text-right">
<p class="text-[9px] tracking-widest uppercase text-ginza-gold mb-0.5">The Craft</p>
<p class="font-cormorant italic text-lg">Omakase Sushi</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative flex-1 h-52 overflow-hidden group">
<img alt="A5 Wagyu" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" src="/images/wagyu.jpg"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-ginza-black/70"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-4">
<p class="text-[9px] tracking-widest uppercase text-ginza-gold mb-0.5">The Ritual</p>
<p class="font-cormorant italic text-lg">A5 Wagyu</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- OUR STORY -->
<section class="reveal py-20 bg-ginza-black border-t border-ginza-gold/10" id="story">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8">
<div class="text-center mb-12">
<p class="section-label mb-4">Our Story</p>
<h3 class="font-cormorant italic text-3xl leading-snug">The Story Begins in 1962</h3>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-10">
<div class="flex-shrink-0 text-center">
<div class="year-badge">1962</div>
<div class="w-px h-16 bg-ginza-gold/20 mx-auto mt-2"></div>
</div>
<div class="pt-3">
<p class="text-sm font-light leading-relaxed text-ginza-ivory/70">
The first generation started this journey as a Wagyu merchant. A craftsman who faced cattle, discerned the quality of meat, and honed his skills. Since then, the family business expanded to meat wholesale, butcher shops, and the food industry. I was raised alongside meat as the fifth generation.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative mb-10 pl-6 border-l border-ginza-gold/30">
<p class="font-cormorant italic text-xl leading-relaxed text-ginza-ivory/90 mb-3">
"Wagyu was never a 'special occasion treat' for me. I have known its taste since I was a child and it was always close to me."
</p>
<p class="text-[10px] font-josefin tracking-widest text-ginza-gold/60 uppercase">— 5th Generation Owner</p>
</div>
<div class="mb-8">
<p class="section-label mb-3">The Turning Point</p>
<p class="text-sm font-light leading-relaxed text-ginza-ivory/70 mb-4">
However, in my 30s, when I visited America, that feeling was greatly shaken. The "WAGYU" I encountered there was completely different from the Wagyu I knew. Cattle from Australia and America were circulated as "Wagyu," and many people smiled as they ate, saying, "Is this Wagyu?"
</p>
<p class="text-sm font-light leading-relaxed text-ginza-ivory/70">
Seeing that scene brought me both surprise and frustration. As the fifth generation, I decided to deliver the "real Wagyu" to the world once again — and opened this restaurant in the heart of Tokyo.
</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-ginza-gold/5 border border-ginza-gold/15 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8">
<p class="section-label mb-3">Our Commitment to Quality</p>
<p class="text-sm font-light leading-relaxed text-ginza-ivory/70">
I visit livestock farms all over Japan and purchase only Wagyu that I truly accept by the whole head. Not the industrially fattened Wagyu with excessive fat — rather, Wagyu raised healthily with <span class="text-ginza-gold/90">umami and tenderness in the meat itself, not just in the fat.</span> This philosophy carries through every dish we serve.
</p>
</div>
<div class="mb-4">
<p class="section-label mb-3">For Everyone in the World</p>
<p class="text-sm font-light leading-relaxed text-ginza-ivory/70">
I personally select Wagyu processed at trusted suppliers in Japan. This restaurant was born to share authentic Japanese food culture with everyone — regardless of nationality, religion, age, or gender.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<div class="relative h-48 overflow-hidden">
<img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0" style="background:linear-gradient(to bottom, #090909 0%, transparent 30%, transparent 70%, #090909 100%);"></div>
<div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
<p class="font-cormorant italic text-2xl text-ginza-ivory/80 tracking-widest">— Course Selection —</p>
</div>
</div>

<!-- COURSE SELECTION -->
<section class="reveal py-16 bg-ginza-black" id="courses">
<div class="px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-10">
<div class="rounded-xl p-4 text-center" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(201,169,110,0.15) 0%,rgba(201,169,110,0.05) 100%); border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.35);">
<p class="font-cormorant italic text-2xl text-ginza-gold mb-1">Only 5%</p>
<p class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-ginza-ivory/60">of the market</p>
<p class="text-[10px] text-ginza-ivory/40 mt-1">Ultra-rare lean Wagyu</p>
</div>
<div class="rounded-xl p-4 text-center" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(201,169,110,0.15) 0%,rgba(201,169,110,0.05) 100%); border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.35);">
